{"tid":152550,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來寂寞的時候，所有的人都一樣。","createTime":"2017-03-11T20:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T17:54:24.000Z","uid":59006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2837b5f1df321462e0d7b3c0bd60225b9d98c11","tid":152550,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T20:30:48.000Z","msg":"　　<br />\n我曾經愛上一個人，我想知道她到底喜不喜歡我。我發現這個機器人很像她，我開始嘗試在她身上尋找答案。我不斷的嘗試，但她始終沒有反應。在我最失望的時候我想過放棄，可很快我又繼續。慢慢的我開始懷疑自己，她對你沒有反應未必是因為它反映遲鈍，也許是因為她對你沒有感覺，到最後終於明白，有些事情不能勉強，而我可以做的就是放棄。"},{"pid":"1813dac5d1fde7b26cc3beec7ce8ec24eb9dec3a","tid":152550,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T20:32:55.000Z","msg":"其實愛情是有時間性的，認識得太早或太晚都是不行的，如果我在另一個時間或空間認識她，這個結局也許會不一樣"},{"pid":"35963bb26bcc129b4d977fbb3c7b40dabc323ad8","tid":152550,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T20:33:08.000Z","msg":"都好既 <br />\n好在你地呢D毒男淨係識性幻想唔會危害到呢個社會 <br />\n但係我就替你地老豆老母唔抵囉 <br />\n養隻狗都識對你擺下尾吠兩聲同你玩最多幾個月發一次情 <br />\n養你地件廢人就乜向左走向右走都唔識仲要日日都發情 <br />\n屌<br />\n不過人地老豆老母既事我都管唔來喇 <br />\n下次你地打j記住去d隱閉既地方唔好嚇親其他人 <br />\n食飯就唔好食咁多喇 <br />\n食埋食埋咪又係j左出來? <br />\n呢個世界好多人無飯食要餓死 <br />\n但你地呢d廢人只係識食飯用來j <br />\n唉, 無眼睇"},{"pid":"5f96a3257716b736187480bd884bff921251b38e","tid":152550,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T20:33:52.000Z","msg":"每個人都會經歷這個階段，看見一座山，就想知道山後面是什麼。我很想告訴他，可能翻過去山後面，你會發覺沒有什麼特別，回頭看會覺得這邊更好。"},{"pid":"71dc3005dc1d0ef50e055111b46002deeee1d6a5","tid":152550,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T20:34:38.000Z","msg":"不知道從什麼時候開始，在什麼東西上面都有個日期，秋刀魚會過期，肉罐頭會過期，連保鮮紙都會過期，我開始懷疑，在這個世界上，還有什麼東西是不會過期的？"},{"pid":"6c02fb2360a6487a7ec92f16307c4046edc8fcca","tid":152550,"uid":44118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T21:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344b83830f9f880d09b8a29326910358d211213b","tid":152550,"uid":33040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T02:24:58.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"6ffc253b105f34945babbaec8e025f39c7a8621b","tid":152550,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T07:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lm</blockquote><br />\n其實了解一個人並不代表什麼，人是會變的，今天他喜歡鳳梨，明天他可以喜歡別的。"},{"pid":"88937f44bbd85c29e29cf742b48f9dd5249eb2bb","tid":152550,"uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> sbt,dude"},{"pid":"febf33fc801d46755e3ed885f1ed12512c051e61","tid":152550,"uid":62859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:41:34.000Z","msg":"其實寂寞 又有咩可怕喎"},{"pid":"968914797c293b5296a2b819a4afd7bec5bd4001","tid":152550,"uid":47170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:53:44.000Z","msg":"何寶榮 黎耀輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f91ec18660712842073a7854fcc5a31e07d0c1","tid":152550,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:55:20.000Z","msg":"你俾錢我 我幫你製造一個初戀既感覺"},{"pid":"39a30d9927d0292189ea59532422121850bffd8b","tid":152550,"uid":9019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:56:49.000Z","msg":"竟然而家先有人知樓豬講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a84f42aaca26e4705494f0939a1015c98fab5e","tid":152550,"uid":9019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>何寶榮 黎耀輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n周慕雲 蘇麗珍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc0f048470d85cc17ba040f328a8f72c9894927","tid":152550,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>何寶榮 黎耀輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如我哋從頭嚟過啊"},{"pid":"a4ae0ecb611a71757cc24b27f6af4252407f9489","tid":152550,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:08:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然而家先有人知樓豬講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494bcea70da568f40bb847d0e3fa3c939ca85aca","tid":152550,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你俾錢我 我幫你製造一個初戀既感覺</blockquote><br />\n我真心架"},{"pid":"7ee4ae481f6dd1f1700a13bdcad6c845288de247","tid":152550,"uid":47170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>何寶榮 黎耀輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如我哋從頭嚟過啊</blockquote><br />\n我好撚後悔啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372e10319ef47d83c4d918e118d9332dfc9ec98c","tid":152550,"uid":47170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:28:29.000Z","msg":"我以前以為一分鐘很快就會過去，其實是可以很長的。有一天有個人指著手錶跟我說，他說會因為那一分鐘而永遠記住我，那時候我覺得很動聽&hellip;&hellip;但現在我看著時鐘，我就告訴自己，我要從這一分鐘開始忘掉這個人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xc4Dp2g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxc4Dp2g.jpg&h=62af0c43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a87b337a7276f631755987687af429380c67f85","tid":152550,"uid":59006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>何寶榮 黎耀輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如我哋從頭嚟過啊</blockquote><br />\n我好撚後悔啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當你不能夠再擁有，你唯一可以做的，就是令自己不要忘記。"},{"pid":"2ebe0118835bfb63da3c56ba2574bfc535307147","tid":152550,"uid":47170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T10:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>何寶榮 黎耀輝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如我哋從頭嚟過啊</blockquote><br />\n我好撚後悔啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當你不能夠再擁有，你唯一可以做的，就是令自己不要忘記。</blockquote><br />\n醉生夢死，不過是她跟我開的一個玩笑。有些事情你越想忘記，就會記得越牢"},{"pid":"16a32482e4474c0bac56bc0509b5dda29e74e791","tid":152550,"uid":59006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T17:54:24.000Z","msg":"回憶是潮濕的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}